data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!! COME SEE THIS GREAT HOUSE WITH DUAL MASTER BEDROOMS in this Cibolo home!  New vinyl plank floors and carpet!  New interior paint throughout! Large home ready for quick move-in!  Downstairs has great use of space!! Separate formal dining, island kitchen w/ granite c'tops, custom 42in cabinets, nice appliances and open to 2-story living rm w/ rock fireplace & eat-in area. Lg utility rm/ pantry space off kitchen. Full Master bedroom down featuring full bath w/ shower only & lg walk-in closet.  Upstairs features loft/gameroom, 4 spacious bedrooms PLUS a 2nd Master BR with an exec style bath & walk-in closet.  Enclosed back patio/sunroom plus patio slab compliment this smaller in size yard.
